{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"http://ghost.local:8000","title":"Ghost Docs","description":"Everything you need to know about working with the Ghost professional publishing platform."}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"body_class","date":"2018-10-01","date_pretty":"01 October, 2018","path":null,"meta_title":"Ghost Handlebars Theme Helpers: body_class","meta_description":"Learn how to target specific pages of your Ghost publication with styles. Read more about Ghost themes! ðŸ‘»","image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":"handlebars","toc":null,"keywords":["api","handlebars","themes","helpers"]},"html":"<p>Usage: <code class=\"language-text\">{{body_class}}</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"description\"><a href=\"#description\" aria-label=\"description permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Description</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">{{body_class}}</code> â€“ outputs dynamic CSS classes intended for the <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;body&gt;</code> tag in your <code class=\"language-text\">default.hbs</code> or other layout file, and is useful for targeting specific pages (or contexts) with styles.</p>\n<p>The <code class=\"language-text\">{{body_class}}</code> helper outputs different classes on different pages, depending on what context the page belongs to. For example the home page will get the class <code class=\"language-text\">.home-template</code>, but a single post page would get <code class=\"language-text\">.post-template</code>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"examples\"><a href=\"#e